<a class="text-charcoal dark:text-white text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium leading-normal hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/reviews">한줄평</a>
<a class="text-charcoal dark:text-white text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium leading-normal hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="/mybookshelf">내 서재</a>
</nav>
<button id="theme-toggle" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-9 h-9 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 rounded-full border border-charcoal/10 dark:border-white/10 hover:bg-charcoal/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors" aria-label="다크모드 전환">
