          <p id="modal-book-publisher" class="text-charcoal/40 dark:text-white/40 text-xs sm:text-sm mb-2 sm:mb-3">{bookPublisher}{bookPubdate ? ` (${bookPubdate.slice(0,4)})` : ''}</p>
